metadata.name: Lucky Buddha Egg
metadata.description: Let me tell you a story about the Lucky Buddha Egg. He is not a regular egg. He is an egg that upon mint out will turn into a barcode that will result in a Cashapp or Ethereum claim. Someone will get this egg. Someone will access a nice surprise cash amount greater than $1000.00. Act fast, you must own one to take part in this race to win. Ready. Set. Go!
